● You can banish 1 LIGHT monster from your Graveyard, then target 1 monster you control; it gains 500 ATK until the end of your opponent''s turn.', 'Add 1 Level 4 Light Warrior-Type', 'Add 500 atk', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '');
